
Dockerfile.cudaq-qiskit  is used to work on PM by Jan & Martin


To erase all podman files for private images:
rm -rf $SCRATCH/storage

To erase all podman files for public images:
Marin:  rm -rf  /global/cfs/cdirs/nintern/gzquse/podman_common/

Jan: rm -rf /global/cfs/cdirs/nstaff/balewski/podman_common/

Possible method of enabling GPU on MacOS
https://sinrega.org/2024-03-06-enabling-containers-gpu-macos/

Image compilation on PM, work for Jan & Martin the same way

time  ./podman-hpc-build.sh -f Dockerfile.cudaq-qiskit-ompi-full -t cudaquanmpi-qiskit:p7